name: Vol 1., Ch.6: Memory Games
description: Tipsy twister was not such a good idea for Tiara, who suffered from terrible coordination. After the sixth drink she could barely stand up and felt quite dizzy. “Are you feeling ok?” asked Clair. As she turned around Tiara noticed Claire was no longer wearing her pajamas, and just covered by her small pink panties. Soon she noticed she was also almost completly naked, as were the rest of the girls. She felt an intense confusion for a second, but then let go, feeling extremely tired.
